UNITED STATES ex rel. Sotiouras CHRISTOULAS, Relator-Appellant, v. Henry H. CURRAN, as Commissioner, etc., Respondent-Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 17, 1926.) No. 289. F. E. Hamilton, of New York City, for appellant. Emory R. Buckner, U. S. Atty. (N. R. Margold, of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before HOUGH, MANTON, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
